<style>
  .shopify-section-group-header-group,.shopify-section-group-footer-group{display:none!important}
  .ele-page{font-family:Georgia,"Times New Roman",Times,serif;background:#f7f5f2;color:#1a1a1a;min-height:100vh}.ele-wrap{max-width:980px;margin:0 auto;padding:72px 22px}.ele-kicker{color:#2D5016;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.12em;font-weight:800;font-size:13px}.ele-page h1{font-size:clamp(42px,7vw,78px);line-height:.95;letter-spacing:-.06em;margin:14px 0 20px}.ele-page p,.ele-page li{font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;color:#3a3a3a}.ele-card{background:white;border:1px solid #e5dfd6;border-radius:28px;padding:34px;box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(17,17,17,.06)}.ele-card h2{font-size:clamp(30px,4vw,48px);line-height:1;margin:0 0 16px}.ele-cta{display:inline-flex;margin-top:20px;padding:15px 22px;border-radius:999px;background:#2D5016;color:white!important;text-decoration:none;font-weight:900}
</style>
<main class="ele-page">
  <section class="ele-wrap">
    <span class="ele-kicker">Download Your Tour Photos (Free)</span>
    <h1>Found Your Magical Moments!</h1>
    <p>We provide 100% free professional photography for all our eco-travelers. Your high-definition memories are uploaded within 72 hours and securely kept for 90 days.</p>
    <div class="ele-card">
      <h2>How to download</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>Click the button below to visit our official Facebook Page.</li>
        <li>Find the album from your tour date, grouped by day.</li>
        <li>Download your high-resolution photos with the elephants for free.</li>
      </ol>
      <p>If you share these photos on social media and tag us, or leave a kind review, it is one of the most meaningful ways to support our elephant welfare work.</p>
      <a class="ele-cta" href="https://www.facebook.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open Official Facebook Page</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
{% schema %}{"name":"Elephant photos page","settings":[],"presets":[{"name":"Elephant photos page"}]}{% endschema %}
